{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act36side", "eventName": "泰拉飯", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DT-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "羅德島大食堂", "storyInfo": "終於登上了羅德島的小隊幾人再次追上了刻俄柏，但是眼前的小刻似乎變得有點奇怪……\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_laccolith", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "匯總一下我們一路上收集的有關羅德島的情報吧。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先，大鮑勃和大祭司都認為羅德島可以幫助我們……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其次，小刻也說這裡有個叫作“博士”的人一定知道怎麼解決我們的問題……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及，我們這次好像終於真的接近那艘艦船了！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望那裡真的有能解決我們問題的方法……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們快過來看！", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_0_rhodes3", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在奇爾查克的呼喊下，三人走到了懸崖邊，那一瞬間，他們就理解了奇爾查克的語氣為什麼會有點著急。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是一艘過於巨大的陸上艦船。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在陸地上航行，卻比他們見過的任何一艘水上船隻都要龐大。"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一座鋼鐵巨構。一座城市。一座……迷宮。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是——“羅德島”。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_laccolith", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真的是一艘在陸地行駛的艦船啊。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們真的能在那裡找到回去的路嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "首先，我覺得我們應該考慮的是——", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們該怎麼進去？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從這裡我甚至看不見它的入口。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#6$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你們看！那邊好像有一支隊伍在靠近羅德島。", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來好像是一支商隊。", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "商隊……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "各位，我們去和他們聊聊吧？看他們是否願意帶我們進去。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodeslowerdeck", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們回來了。", "name": "先鋒幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦了。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事。對了，我們剛剛還遇到了四個來求助的人，穿著打扮都蠻奇怪的，說是和刻俄柏認識，想讓羅德島幫他們回家。", "name": "先鋒幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？回家？", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_090", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大概是這個意思，總之辛苦你給他們帶一下路，我去和外勤部交接了。", "name": "先鋒幹員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "萊歐斯小隊"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好！", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你們是專門來羅德島求助的，應該是要找博士或是阿米婭吧？", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……小刻倒是說過“博士”，我們可能是要找這個人……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能帶我們去見這個博士嗎？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我還需要確認下你們的身分，你們先跟我……", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$book_close", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦哦……！不好意思，我的東西掉了……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《鮑勃的美食指南》？", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們認識大鮑勃？", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我們來這裡吃到的第一頓飯就是他做的。", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#18$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能把那樣堅硬的蟲子處理成一道道美味的食物，老夫很敬佩那個人。", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了……原來他說的“那些朋友”就是你們。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫泥岩，大鮑勃跟我講過你們。當初他們剛決定不再當傭兵，想要換一個活法，但完全不知道開農場的事行不行得通。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "荒野上的農場經常會遭到洗劫，大鮑勃也不認識幾個做生意的人，啤酒做出來也不知道好不好。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你們當時吃他的料理的樣子很幸福，給了他不少信心。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老夫當時並沒有看出來他這樣的窘迫……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……那他現在怎麼樣……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，我們也很久沒見過了。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是聽說他後來源石蟲啤酒廠經營得很好，賺了不少錢，也過上好日子了。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但後來又聽說好像是賺錢的時候得罪了當地政府，說是稅務還是什麼問題，被關進監獄裡了。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監獄？那他們現在還好嗎……？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#11$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前段時間又聽說他們好像越獄還是保釋出來了，人沒什麼問題。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯？嗯……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越獄啊……", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#6$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再聽說到的就是他們好像在薩米開了家雜貨店，生意不錯呢。", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的是……很有毅力地在生活啊……", "name": "先西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4143_sensi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，先跟我來吧，我們坐電梯上去……", "name": "泥岩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "電梯……？就是這個鐵盒子嗎……？它怎麼用？", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#8$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來也像是一個魔法器具……", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "