, "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassdooropen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼一開門全都變了？！", "name": "萊歐斯小隊"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是哪裡？剛剛發生了什麼？", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#9$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼這裡看起來更像是個迷宮啊……", "name": "萊歐斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_4142_laios_1#16$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……果然是你。", "name": "艾爾啟"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是薩米的獨眼巨人……？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獨眼巨人？！為什麼奇爾查克你會——", "name": "瑪露希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4141_marcil_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你出現在這裡，該不會是因為你又看到了什麼吧？", "name": "奇爾查克"}, "figure_art": "avg_4144_chilc_1#15$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_969_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190